        <p>Call us at +91 98765 43210 or message at support@bauadadhabaa.com â€” our team will respond faster than your order arrives!</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline-light">Contact Us</a>
     </div>
     <div class="contact-img"></div>
</div>

